---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn about Pythia Insights and our approach to financial intelligence">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">About Us</span>
      <h1>Financial Clarity for the Modern Business</h1>
      <p class="page-intro">We started Pythia because too many growing businesses are flying blind‚Äîmaking million-dollar decisions with spreadsheet-level visibility.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-content">
        <h2>Why "Pythia"?</h2>
        <p>In ancient Greece, the Pythia was the Oracle of Delphi‚Äîthe source of clarity and foresight for leaders facing their most important decisions.</p>
        <p>That's the role we aim to fill for modern businesses. Not mystical prophecy, but clear-eyed analysis that helps you see what's coming and prepare for it.</p>
        <p>We believe every growing business deserves access to the kind of financial intelligence that Fortune 500 companies take for granted. Our job is to make that accessible, practical, and actionable.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="philosophy">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Our Philosophy</span>
        <h2>How We Think About Finance</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="philosophy-grid">
        <div class="philosophy-card">
          <h3>Forward, Not Backward</h3>
          <p>Historical financials are table stakes. We focus on what's coming‚Äîforecasts that drive action, not just reports that explain the past.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-card">
          <h3>Insight, Not Just Data</h3>
          <p>Anyone can pull numbers from a system. We turn those numbers into stories that lead to better decisions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-card">
          <h3>Partnership, Not Vendors</h3>
          <p>We succeed when you succeed. That means understanding your business deeply and caring about outcomes, not just deliverables.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-card">
          <h3>Build to Scale</h3>
          <p>Every process and system we implement is designed to grow with you. No rebuilding from scratch when you hit the next stage.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="approach">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="approach-content">
        <span class="section-label">Our Approach</span>
        <h2>Modern Finance for Modern Business</h2>
        <p>The financial function has evolved. Spreadsheets and month-end reports aren't enough anymore. We bring modern tools and methodologies to help you:</p>
        <div class="approach-grid">
          <div class="approach-item">
            <div class="approach-icon">‚ö°</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Move Faster</h4>
              <p>Real-time data and automated workflows mean you're not waiting weeks for answers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="approach-item">
            <div class="approach-icon">üéØ</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Decide Better</h4>
              <p>Clear frameworks and scenario analysis take the guesswork out of big decisions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="approach-item">
            <div class="approach-icon">üìà</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Scale Confidently</h4>
              <p>Financial systems that grow with you, not ones you'll outgrow in 18 months.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="approach-item">
            <div class="approach-icon">üîç</div>
            <div>
              <h4>See Clearly</h4>
              <p>Dashboards and KPIs that tell the truth about what's really happening.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="values">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">What We Value</span>
        <h2>Principles That Guide Us</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="values-list">
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-number">01</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Clarity Over Complexity</h3>
            <p>Simple solutions that work beat elegant solutions that don't. We optimize for understanding and action.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-number">02</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Ownership Mentality</h3>
            <p>We treat your business like our own. That means telling you hard truths and pushing back when needed.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-number">03</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Continuous Improvement</h3>
            <p>Good enough today isn't good enough tomorrow. We're always looking for better ways to serve you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-number">04</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Transparent Communication</h3>
            <p>No jargon, no surprises. You'll always know what we're doing, why we're doing it, and what it costs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Let's Talk About Your Business</h2>
        <p>Whether you're trying to solve a specific problem or just want a clearer picture of your finances, we're here to help.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a Conversation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 180px 0 100px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e8ecf1 100%);
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .page-intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .story {
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .story-content {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .story-content h2 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .story-content p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .philosophy {
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .philosophy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .philosophy-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  }

  .philosophy-card h3 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .philosophy-card p {
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .approach {
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .approach-content h2 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .approach-content > p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .approach-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .approach-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .approach-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .approach-item h4 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .approach-item p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .values {
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .values .section-label {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .values .section-header h2 {
    color: white;
  }

  .values-list {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .value-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 32px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .value-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .value-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.5;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 60px;
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .value-item p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  }

  .cta {
    background: var(--primary);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .cta-content {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .cta p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 140px 0 60px;
    }

    .value-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .value-number {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
